Go to https://github.com/libsdl-org/SDL/releases/tag/release-2.26.1

download the one that says SDL2-devel-vc.zip

extract the contents of the zip to the root of your c drive

rename the folder to SDL2

download microsoft  visual studio  at https://visualstudio.microsoft.com/downloads/ if you don't have it already setup
set it up, not to important, and when it asks you to open a new file select the clone repository and then clone this repository using the link

https://github.com/nixz-leon/sdl_lin_proj.git

